snippet.title: JoJo's Bizarre Adventure: All-Star Battle R – Part 5 Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Are you ready to become top of the chain in Passione? 

Golden Wind has stormed into JoJo's Bizarre Adventure: All-Star Battle R and the Bucciarati gang is going to do whatever it takes to protect Trish Una against the likes of Diavolo and any other gang members who stand up to them!

Pre-Order now! http://www.jojoasbr.com

Follow JoJo Games:
Twitter/X: https://twitter.com/jojo_games  
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/jojo_games/

#JOJO #JJBA #ALLSTARBATTLER
